“Current and former Trump officials say that Trump can react like a volcano to negative press clippings, especially those with damaging leaks, and that he ’ s fixated on finding out where they come from.
This is what happened at the end of February, when someone maliciously gave the president a printed copy of an article by GotNews.com, the website of the Internet ’ s provocateur Charles C. Johnson, accusing Deputy Chief of Staff Katie Walsh of being “the source behind a pile of leaks ” in the White House.
