Deutsche Bahn: Group tests "comfort check"
It is a moment that almost everyone has experienced before: you sit in the train and sleep without a clue.
Or you are absorbed in your work and just have an ingenious thought.
And then: pufff.
If the conductor comes and wakes you up rudely or tears the passenger out of the workflow.
Ticket inspection.
