Also for the children.
"They have a well-known force in kindergarten, a person who is familiar to them, and not constantly changing people".
This continuity is important for the children.
The cleaning of the daycare facilities – previously also the job of the kitchen staff – will in future be carried out by special cleaning personnel.
This variant - the separation of cleaning and kitchen service - has apart from the quality improvement of the kitchen achievement also the charm, which it turned out in the cost comparison between self-direction and outsourcing for the city as the most economical, reads it from the press office.
